{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"95392-uh-oh","title":"Aïe !","description":"Que se passe-t-il lorsque tu t'approches trop près de certains animaux ou de certaines plantes ? Ils utilisent des astuces pour se protéger du danger. Découvre-les dans ce petit livre très drôle.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Kingshuk Chaudhary"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/95392-uh-oh"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725074/size3/f5dbe41d34eb61fdb426b974dff0fa24.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725074/size6/f5dbe41d34eb61fdb426b974dff0fa24.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113672/size6/abd8263d9e6c6a6cd9610304c21f7f40.jpg","text":"Coucou ! Je suis très rapide !","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113673/size6/fc910ab38501babc4303a60abe24581b.jpg","text":"Essaie de toucher ma queue, pour voir.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113674/size6/39eb05e2f8b739437c9dc00e92896063.jpg","text":"Oh ! Oh !","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120643/size6/16eaf7ef6d4ca62538dac37c3dd984d0.jpg","text":"Ne touche pas mes feuilles, s'il te plaît.\nJe suis en train d'admirer les nuages.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/119106/size6/257b37b785feb90083149735b3b5b8de.jpg","text":"Oh, non !","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113677/size6/a4cba391c2d6169a6860d53fd1d49056.jpg","text":"Je ne suis pas toujours aussi petit.\nRegarde ce qu'il se passe si tu cries PLOUF !","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113678/size6/2180481e266b8be1d0c48d78cde6cc4f.jpg","text":"Plop !","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/119108/size6/0c71318dbcd5e190c57b710398be1ee9.jpg","text":"Je n'ai peur de rien. Même pas des lions.\nAllez, RRRRUGIT de toutes tes forces.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113680/size6/d95d9de4c59031e9398bcfdf0830c3b2.jpg","text":"Klonk !","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113681/size6/aaa029c9b9c3a3b8abf478e49fb15be1.jpg","text":"Quand j'entends des chansons, il se passe un drôle de truc.\nAlors, ne me chante rien, s'il te plaît.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/114329/size6/311565ca867f926988b3e0f3a0dee22a.jpg","text":"Pfouiiit !","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120366/size6/af07ec6bae080440f4fb5ee4fb56926e.jpg","text":"Fais-moi ta plus horrible grimace.\nAllez !","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120365/size6/490781bf6864803b8ca7eddf884e8de9.jpg","text":"Aaaah !","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113684/size6/3bdd776549473b77c76fd5b059d6135c.jpg","text":"Je dois rester calme, mais je ne me souviens plus pourquoi.\nNe fais pas de gestes brusques, d'accord ?","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113685/size6/82ab1931d481082535428f6951f35aaa.jpg","text":"Oh ! Oh !","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130111/size6/f7f0c83769c3725cbeacd39a92968186.jpg","text":"DÉCOUVRE LES PERSONNAGES\nLézard\nPorc-épic\nCaméléon\nPangolin\nPoisson-globe\nPieuvre\nMimosa pudique","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":136}}